findPasswordHash: select password from Users where username = ? or email = ?
findBySearchTerm: select  id, username,  email, name from Users  where ( select ( @SearchParam := CONCAT("%",?,"%"))) or upper(username) like @SearchParam COLLATE utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci or upper(email) like @SearchParam COLLATE utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci or upper(name) like @SearchParam COLLATE utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci
findByUsername: select id, username,  email, name from Users where username = ? or email = ?
findByWallet: select U.id, username,  email, name, address as wallet from Users U join Wallets W on U.id = W.userId  where address = ?
findById: select id, username,  email, name from Users  where id = ?
listAll: select U.id, username,  email, name as firstName, if(U.banned, 'TRUE', 'FALSE' ) as banned, description, avatarHash, avatarExtension, U.createdAt, roleId, if(emailVerified, 'TRUE', 'FALSE' ) as emailVerified, if(subscribed, 'TRUE', 'FALSE' ) as subscribed, title, websiteUrl,  bannerExtension, bannerHash, if(shadowBanned, 'TRUE', 'FALSE' ) as shadowBanned, W.address as wallet from Users U left join Wallets W on U.id = W.userId
